### ERROR TIPS
### Errors when inserting items into a full inventory
- Ensure the inventory is not full before attempting to insert items
### Errors when using extracting but being too far
- Not found in this execution log
### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Not found in this execution log
### Errors when inserter is waiting for source items
- Ensure the inserter has source items to pick up before attempting to insert items
### Errors when chest is full
- Ensure the chest is not full before attempting to insert items into it
### Errors when furnace has no ingredients to smelt
- Ensure the furnace has ingredients to smelt before attempting to smelt
### Errors when boiler is out of fuel
- Ensure the boiler has fuel before attempting to use it
### Errors when steam engine has no input liquid
- Ensure the steam engine has input liquid before attempting to use it
### Errors when pipe has no fluid present in connections
- Ensure the pipe has fluid present in connections before attempting to use it
